metadata.name: The End Is Near #1/4
metadata.description:
In the shadows of a world crumbling apart, a solitary car lay abandoned, its once-gleaming paint now dulled by the ravages of time and despair. As the days dwindled away, whispers spread among the survivors, telling the tale of this forsaken vehicle and its enigmatic message.

Some spoke of a desperate family who had once sought refuge in the car, only to vanish without a trace. The car's haunting message, "The end is near," had become the stuff of legend, an ominous prophecy that filled the hearts of those who gazed upon it with dread and unease.
